                    <msContents>  
                        <summary>Minhāj al-vuṣūl ilá ʿilm al-ʾuṣūl is the title of one of the works written by Qāz̤ī Bayz̤āvī on the principles of Islamic jurisprudence
                            and presented in the form of an introduction and seven books. Many commentaries have been written on this work, including 'Sirāj-i Vahhāj'
                            by Aḥmad bin Ḥasan Jārbardī (746 Qamarī) and 'Nahāyat al-Sūl fī Sharḥ Minhāj al-vuṣūl' by Asnavī. There is allegedly another commentary on this work
                            called 'al-Ḥanafīyah lil-minhāj ʿalá ḥal al-matn', whose author was not known based on the avaialble sources. The present copy is a summary of the
                            aforementioned commentary, whose author has remained unknown too.</summary>
                        <msItem>
                            <textLang mainLang="ara">Arabic</textLang>
                            <note type="content-genre">Principles of Islamic jurisprudence</note>
                            <title xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc">Ikhtiṣār al-ḥanafīyah lil-minhāj ʿalá ḥal al-matn</title>
                            <title xml:lang="ara">اختصار الحنفیه للمنهاج علی حل المتن</title>
                            <author>
                                <persName xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Unknown.</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc" type="alt"></persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="ara"></persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="ara" type="alt"></persName>
                                <addName xml:lang="ara" type="laqab"/>
                                <addName xml:lang="ara" type="kunyah"/>
                                <addName xml:lang="ara" type="khitab"/>
                                <addName xml:lang="ara" type="nisbah"/>
                            </author>
                            <note></note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="ara">بسمله، حمدله، و بعد… من لم یظن فی قوله الا محض الخیر الی اختصار الشرح المسمی بالحنفیه للمنهاج
                            علی حل المتن و نصرة المذهب وشیی من الاسوله…</incipit>
                            <explicit xml:lang="ara" defective="true">… لا ینسخ سیی من الادلة و لا ینسخ من الادلة به ایضا اما النص والاجماع ای لانها…</explicit> 
                            <colophon xml:lang="ara">None.</colophon>
